						<summary>

						<p>On a stone in the Veṅkaṭaramaṇasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>The record is dated Śaka 1592, <hi rend="italic">Sādhāraṇa, Jyēshṭha,</hi> śu. 15, corresponding to A.D. 1670, May 24.</p>						

						<p>Incomplete. Mentions god Veṅkaṭēśvara of Velalūru and seems to refer to the <hi rend="italic">ratha[mahōtsava*]</hi> of the deity.</p>						

