<p>Figures of Sun, Vaḍagalai-nāmam, crescent moon.</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>bhyudaya śālivā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>hana śakavarṣaṁbbu 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>lu 1592 pravarta(rdha) 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>māna sādhāraṇa saṁ 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vvatsara jyēṣṭha śu 15 
<lb n="7"/>śrīmadakhilāṁ 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍakōṭi brahmāṁ 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḍḍanāyaka vēda vē 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>dāṁtta(ta)vēdya purā 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṇa puruṣōttamu 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>laina velalūri śrī 
<lb n="13" break="no"/><unclear>veṁ</unclear>kaṭēśvarla ratha 
</p>

<p>Incomplete.</p>

